// ────────────── Output Configuration ──────────────
// You can run `niri msg outputs` to get the correct name for your displays.
// You will have to remove "/-" and edit it before it takes effect.
// https://github.com/YaLTeR/niri/wiki/Configuration:-Outputs

// Pin the laptop panel at origin; any external output is auto-placed to its
// right (niri appends unpositioned outputs to the right of positioned ones).
// This keeps "external on the right" stable regardless of the external's
// resolution/scale and without relying on the unstable connector name.
output "eDP-1" {
    position x=0 y=0
}